KitKat::

She looked to Destructor. "You take the next CR chamber. I will hold 
out untill another one is available." Her levels were dropping 
rapidly.  She opened her comlink to SharpClaw. "Hey, lazy bolts, you 
aobut done with that chamber, we have wounded bots that need it. 
There are only so many chambers you know." she said, with a slight 
chuckle in her voice. She groaned softly as her wounds almost caused 
her to double over.
